## Summary

**Two changes, one new file:**

1. **`api/v1beta1/clusterpodplacementconfig_webhook.go`** — Remove the `"errors"` import (no longer needed). Replace the inline duplicate-checking loop in `validate()` with a single call to `cppc.Spec.Plugins.NodeAffinityScoring.ValidateArchitecturesSet()`. Both `ValidateCreate` and `ValidateUpdate` already delegate to `validate()`, so both paths get the check.

2. **`api/v1beta1/clusterpodplacementconfig_webhook_test.go`** (new) — Table-driven test covering: nil plugins, nil nodeAffinityScoring, unique architectures, single architecture, exact duplicates, and duplicates among multiple entries. Each case exercises both `ValidateCreate` and `ValidateUpdate`.
